title: Tweety Valentine Cuckold
description: Tweety has been discovered attempting to copy her flame at both finishes. In any case, what were the odds that her significant other would keep running into her new beau at some arbitrary Hollywood gathering? Most likely it's a sign from paradise, or no less than a sign from Tweety's mystery true inner being. She realizes this should happen. That is the reason she laughs in the face of any potential risk and acquaints her better half with the dark man who's going to father her infants!
